«Wild Alchemist» is a video slot with five reels and fifteen paylines. 

Welcome to the magical world of «Wild Alchemist»! Are you ready to dive into a mysterious world of arcane knowledge and alchemical experiments? Be quick, our Alchemist has already solved the riddle of wealth, and he can’t wait to share the truth with you!
 

**How to play «Wild Alchemist»?**

Choose the number of active paylines (from 1 to 15) and place your bets! Your success and winnings depend directly on the number of active paylines you select, your line bet or your credit denomination. Click the «i» (info) button to open the paytable and learn more about all the winning combinations and rules of this slot.
 

**Scatter- and wild- symbols in this game:** 

«ALCHEMIST» is the scatter-symbol in «Wild Alchemist» slot. The scatter-symbol only appears on 2, 3 and 4 reels. «ALCHEMIST» symbols don’t need to appear on one selected payline. «CAULDRON» is the wild-symbol in this game. Here it substitutes all symbols except for the «ALCHEMIST» (our scatter symbol) and the «BOOK» symbol.
 

**In «Wild Alchemist» there are certain conditions for winning combinations:**
 

Combination is a winning one, if the same symbols start on the left or right side of the line, either from left to right or from right to left.
Combination is a winning one, if it appears on an active line.
Only the highest combination on a line is paid.

**Doubling in «Wild Alchemist»:**

You can increase your winnings on any of the winning combinations. To do this, click on the «GAMBLE» button - you will be taken to an additional game. Here you must guess the colour (red or black) or the suit of the card. Choose a card. If the colour of your chosen card matches the colour of the opening card - your winnings are doubled, and if the suit is matched - your winnings are multiplied by 4! After that, you can continue catching your luck or take your winnings.
 

**«Wild Alchemist» Bonus game:**

The fall of 3 «ALCHEMIST» symbols on reels 2, 3 and 4 triggers the bonus game. New window opens up with five flasks for you to decide from. Note that Alchemist is initially wearing a protective mask - in Bonus game this element acts as an extra chance for another try after an unsuccessful choice (like an extra «life» of Alchemist). If Alchemist successfully pours the liquid from all the flasks, you move into the Super-Bonus game.
 

**«Wild Alchemist» Super-Bonus gam**e:

Here, a new window with five crystals opens in front of you. Find the «lucky crystal» which will bring you one of the prizes: «x50», «x100» or «x100 and try again». That being said, two of the five crystals always remain fake. Super-Bonus game ends when the crystal is selected. Join the game world of «Wild Alchemist»! Everything here is designed for success and wealth. Our Alchemist has prepared a cauldron of good fortune and luck - see for yourself!

«Wild» is the wild-symbol. It appears on all reels in this video slot. When a wild-symbol appears in front of a regular symbol, it is converted into that symbol with its value, and the corresponding winning is awarded. The combination is considered winning if two halves with the same worth appearing in front of each other and combined into one single banknote.

If 3 banknotes of the Scatter-symbol triggered the Bonus-games: the 1x symbol is removed from the second spin, the 2x symbol is removed from the fourth spin. The 0.25x and 0.5x symbols are absent from the reels during free games.
